{"tid":1468707,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"敵人犯錯就係時機 - 反送中事件簿","createTime":"2019-08-13T20:05:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T07:04:27.000Z","uid":296247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"809d7a92adba2f3049f0ead305b2dba7f3c22542","tid":1468707,"uid":296247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:05:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />運動大大少少發生左好多事，但留意到較多人轉軚嘅主要係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">612+烈士</span></span>、<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">元朗事件</span></span>、<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">社區式催淚彈放題</span></span>，仲有前兩日嘅<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">811屠城</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">612</span></span>後多左一倍人出黎，而<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">元朗</span></span>同<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">社區</span></span>事件非常切身，觸怒好多人。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">811</span>奪去救護員的眼、行刑式近距離開槍、賊贓嫁禍、扮示威者...</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然而，政府同777都係呢啲事之後解釋唔到又hea9記者，令大家嬲到癲，唔少深藍都轉軚，仲有少少道德同是非觀嘅都撐唔落警。<br />\n<br />\n呢幾件事嘅<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">情質都係一樣</span></span>，就係<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">敵人犯錯</span></strong></span>同<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">震驚</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>(1) 敵人犯錯</strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">敵人犯錯就係時機</span></span></strong>，唔好心急要耐性。Plan係敵人犯錯時可以做啲乜，同時唔需要加多腳。<br />\n或者我地<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">主動嘅行動係誘因</span></span></strong>，但以上絕大部份都係黑警同政府犯錯。我地已經好多手足被捕，受傷流血昏迷，再衝出去都唔係辦法。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>(2) 震驚</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">612 +烈士<br />\n721 元朗事件<br />\n811屠城</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n睇返timeline呢三件事震驚好多人，係未見過嘅事發生左，難聽啲講大部份人唔見棺材唔流眼淚。除左係殺到埋身之外，真係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一單恐怖過一單</span></span>。<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>612 開槍</strong></span></span>之後其實好多次都有開槍，但發生得太頻密，好多人似乎已經<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">習慣咗</span></span></strong>。再次挑起好多人條根係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">721</span></strong></span>，至於<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">催淚彈放題</span></span>，如果唔係去到社區，其實啲人都睇慣左，又唔係自己個到發生，真係唔多理。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">811屠城</span></strong></span>- <strong><em><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">first aider中槍、行刑掃射、賊贓嫁禍</span></span></em></strong>，呢啲<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">對好多香港人黎講係<span style=\"color: red;\">第三次世界大戰</span></span></strong>！絕對唔希望再有更震懾嘅事發生，但不幸地發生的話就再會係一個時機。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><br />\n&ldquo;Never interrupt your enemy when he is making a mistake.&rdquo;<br />\n- Napoleon Bonaparte</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n勇武要諗清楚，抖一抖先，大家唔想犧牲更多手足!<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><em>&ldquo;You must not fight too often with one enemy, or you will teach him all your art of war.&rdquo;<br />\n- Napoleon Bonaparte</em></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好想知<strong><ins><span style=\"color: gold;\">之前中槍同受傷手足嘅情況</span></ins></strong>，尤其嚴重個啲，好希望見到update 同被大家知道。唔想不了了知，都係黑警同林鄭造成。大家都會關心的，仲有<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: maroon;\">機場和你飛</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><em>&ldquo;The simplest moves are the best.&rdquo; <br />\n- Napoleon Bonaparte<br />\n</em></span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所有反送中嘅人入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1419582\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1419582</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8a9924433a712a74938cd9cfe61f81bae8f92b09","tid":1468707,"uid":296247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:06:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"61a8c07bff9e4fc9d2c166f5f2953aeb0fa68446","tid":1468707,"uid":83072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:08:51.000Z","msg":"我們在這裏 謹代表不負責任的香港政府 向旅程受阻的各國旅客致歉<br />\n並促使林鄭政府回應示威者訴求"},{"pid":"eb7298e28b447643bf2cb27a1102bee201cf6c31","tid":1468707,"uid":296247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61a8c07bff9e4fc9d2c166f5f2953aeb0fa68446","tid":1468707,"uid":83072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T20:08:51.000Z","msg":"我們在這裏 謹代表不負責任的香港政府 向旅程受阻的各國旅客致歉<br />\n並促使林鄭政府回應示威者訴求"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:51:55.000Z","msg":"要記住取消航班嘅係政府，而唔係和平嘅示威者！"},{"pid":"681ff043a7e3256db44d180e525b09a04829e4b3","tid":1468707,"uid":296247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:52:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e883f79ae9fc03ca21ed2adfddeb65d1457f65fa","tid":1468707,"uid":296247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T03:52:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8f4599f908fa936520e23da9ba2b702dee012fc7","tid":1468707,"uid":2